Class OAConnection

java.lang.Object
  com.viaoa.ds.jdbc.connection.OAConnection

public class OAConnection
extends java.lang.Object

Used to wrap functionality around a java.sql.Connection to offer Statement Pooling. Mostly used internally by ConnectionPool.
